<p dir="auto"><a href="https://github.com/csstools/postcss-plugins/tree/main/plugins/postcss-logical">PostCSS Logical Properties and Values</a>  lets you use logical, rather than physical, direction and dimension mappings in CSS, following the <a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/css-logical-1/" rel="nofollow">CSS Logical Properties and Values</a> specification.</p>
