<p dir="auto">Each direction must be one of the following:</p>
<ul dir="auto">
<li><code>top-to-bottom</code></li>
<li><code>bottom-to-top</code></li>
<li><code>left-to-right</code></li>
<li><code>right-to-left</code></li>
</ul>
<p dir="auto">You can't mix two vertical directions or two horizontal directions so for example <code>top-to-bottom</code> and <code>right-to-left</code> are valid, but <code>top-to-bottom</code> and <code>bottom-to-top</code> are not.</p>
